<h2><a href="http://java.freehep.org">FreeHEP</a>  Java 3D Lego Plot</h2>

<p>The FreeHEP Java3D Lego Plot Demo was written as a test application for the <a href="http://java.freehep.org/lib/freehep/api/org/freehep/j3d/plot/package-summary.html">Java3D
Plotting Package</a>. This package includes three plotting classes: a 2D Lego
Plot, a Surface Plot, and a 3D Scatter Plot. The 3D Lego plotting class also
generates a “line plot” in which each box is replaced by a vertical line for
animation of the plot on slower systems.</p>
<p>The 3D Lego Demo is available for download using Java Web Start. <b>You must
have</b> <a href="http://java.sun.com/products/javawebstart/">Java Web Start 1.0</a>
<b>AND</b> the <a href="http://java.sun.com/products/java-media/3D/index.html">Java
3D extensions</a> <b>already installed</b> on your machine for the download to
work.</p>
<p>Feel free to send comments/suggestions/bug reports to the author, <a href="mailto:joyk@fnal.gov">Joy
Kyriakopulos</a>.</p>

